=\"line\">pic_filename = <span class=\"string\">\"sin.png\"</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">path = <span class=\"string\">'./Matplotlib&amp;#23398;&amp;#20064;&amp;#31508;&amp;#35760;/'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">plt.savefig(<span class=\"string\">'{}{}'</span>.format(path, pic_filename))</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"string\">\"#+caption: &amp;#31532;&amp;#19968;&amp;#24133;&amp;#22270;\"</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">print(<span class=\"string\">\"[[{}{}]]\"</span>.format(path, pic_filename))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"figure\">\n<p><img src=\"./Matplotlib学习笔记/sin.png\" alt=\"sin.png\">\n</p>\n<p><span class=\"figure-number\">Figure 1: </span>第一幅图</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-org5c29c0a\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org5c29c0a\"><span class=\"section-number-2\">3</span> <span class=\"todo TODO\">TODO</span> 特点</h2>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"outline-container-org604c2b0\" class=\"outline-2\">\n<h2 id=\"org604c2b0\"><span class=\"section-number-2\">4</span> 参考</h2>\n<div class=\"outline-text-2\" id=\"text-4\">\n<ul class=\"org-ul\">\n<li><a href=\"http://old.sebug.net/paper/books/scipydoc/index.html\">Python科学计算</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\nLast Updated 2017-05-08 一 11:40.<br>Render by <a href=\"https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-renderer-org\">hexo-renderer-org</a> with <a href=\"http://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/\">Emacs</a> 25.2.1 (<a href=\"http://orgmode.org\">Org</a> mode 9.0.5)\n"}
